body: @z1146335535, the RTX series won't be fully supported until tensorflow-gpu 1.13 is officially released.  Your card needs CUDA 10, this repro relies on CUDA 9.
Tensorflow 1.13 has been pre-released (https://github.com/tensorflow/tensorflow/releases/tag/v1.13.0-rc0) - can anyone with an RTX try running on that?

issue.title: Face extractor suddenly not working

repository.name: DeepFaceLab
repository.description: DeepFaceLab is the leading software for creating deepfakes.
